      <t:profileDesc xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">
         <t:abstract>
            <t:p> The text of the Life of St ʾEwosṭātewos, classified as 'recension β', characterised
               by devotion of <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS1854Amdase">ʿAmda Ṣǝyon I</t:persName> to <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3934Ewostate">ʾEwosṭātewos</t:persName>,
               is believed to represent an elaborated shorter version of  <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4319GadlaEA">Gadla ʾEwosṭātewos</t:ref>, as
               noted in <t:bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/KKZGMGER"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Lusini1993Monachesimo"/><title level="m">Studi sul monachesimo eustaziano (secoli XIV-XV)</title><title level="s">Studi Africanistici</title><author><forename>Gianfrancesco</forename><surname>Lusini</surname></author><pubPlace>Napoli</pubPlace><publisher>Istituto Universitario Orientale</publisher><date>1993</date><series><title level="s">Studi Africanistici</title><biblScope unit="volume">Serie Etiopica, 3</biblScope></series><biblScope unit="volume">Serie Etiopica, 3</biblScope><note type="tags"><note type="tag">bm:Lusini1993Monachesimo</note></note><note type="tag">bm:Lusini1993Monachesimo</note><t:citedRange unit="page">42-43</t:citedRange></t:bibl>.</t:p>
         </t:abstract>
