            <t:div type="textpart" xml:id="Introduction">
               <t:label>Introduction</t:label>
               <t:ab>በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አብ፡ ብሉየ፡ መዋዕል፡ እምቅድመ፡ ዓለም፡ ህልዎቱ፡ ግሩመ፡ ግሩማን፡ በመለኮቱ፡ ልዑለ፡ ልዑላን፡ </t:ab>
               <t:note>The text is taken from <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EMML529">Collegeville, Hill Museum and Manuscript Library, MS EMML no. 529</t:ref>.</t:note>
            </t:div>
            <t:div type="textpart" xml:id="Vita">
               <t:label>Vita</t:label>
               <t:ab>ወጥንኬ፡ ይእዜኒ፡ በረድኤተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ከመ፡ ንጽሐፍ፡ ዜና፡ ገድለ፡ ኂሩቶ፡ ለብፁዕ፡
                  ወለቅዱስ፡ አባ፡ ኤዎስጣቴዎስ፡ </t:ab>
               <t:note>The text is taken from <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EMML529">Collegeville, Hill Museum and Manuscript Library, MS EMML no. 529</t:ref>.</t:note>
            </t:div>
